## 7. Data Security (APP 11)

We protect personal information through:

- Role-based access controls for AI tools{% if ai_access_restricted %} (currently in place){% endif %}
- Encryption of data in transit and at rest
{% if ai_outputs_logged %}
- Logging and monitoring of AI prompts and outputs for security and audit purposes
{% endif %}
- Regular security assessments of AI tool configurations
{% if incident_response_tested %}
- Tested incident response procedures (tabletop exercise completed within past 12 months)
{% else %}
- Incident response procedures (testing recommended)
{% endif %}

### 7.1 Data Retention and Deletion

{% if has_data_retention_policy %}
We maintain a data retention policy that covers AI-processed data and outputs. Personal information is destroyed or de-identified when it is no longer needed for its collected purpose, as required by APP 11.
{% if data_retention_period and data_retention_period != "no_defined_period" %}

Our defined retention ceiling for AI-processed personal information is **{{ data_retention_period | replace("_", " ") }}**. Data is reviewed against this schedule and destroyed or de-identified when the retention period expires or the data is no longer required, whichever comes first.
{% endif %}
{% else %}
**Action Required**: We are developing a data retention policy covering AI-processed data and outputs to ensure compliance with APP 11.
{% endif %}

